  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335680/extras/86071d0722756b9591a6b10cf887608f.poster.avif?t=1626291185\" width=600 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335680/extras/86071d0722756b9591a6b10cf887608f.webm?t=1626291185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335680/extras/86071d0722756b9591a6b10cf887608f.mp4?t=1626291185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Kind Camomille <br><br>A wholesome 3D exploration game about random acts of kindness and the joy of discovery.  Players take control of Camomille, a kind mouse on her way to her dear grandmother 100th birthday. On a relaxing and beautiful journey (that might not be so straight forward) she encounters people in need of a hand.  Along the way, players can uncover small hidden sceneries, find goodies to put in her giftbasket and make that birthday even more special.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A Colorful, Kind and Relaxing Adventure.<br></li><li> No penalties, no death, just take your time.<br></li><li> Collect hidden items for a (non-obligatory) 100% ending.<br></li><li> A short game (about 2 hours), focused on discovery and light puzzle solving.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335680/extras/eba23a6c4a3833f437f715de1d19d1d4.poster.avif?t=1626291185\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335680/extras/eba23a6c4a3833f437f715de1d19d1d4.webm?t=1626291185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335680/extras/eba23a6c4a3833f437f715de1d19d1d4.mp4?t=1626291185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335680/extras/86071d0722756b9591a6b10cf887608f.poster.avif?t=1626291185\" width=600 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335680/extras/86071d0722756b9591a6b10cf887608f.webm?t=1626291185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335680/extras/86071d0722756b9591a6b10cf887608f.mp4?t=1626291185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Kind Camomille <br><br>A wholesome 3D exploration game about random acts of kindness and the joy of discovery.  Players take control of Camomille, a kind mouse on her way to her dear grandmother 100th birthday. On a relaxing and beautiful journey (that might not be so straight forward) she encounters people in need of a hand.  Along the way, players can uncover small hidden sceneries, find goodies to put in her giftbasket and make that birthday even more special.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A Colorful, Kind and Relaxing Adventure.<br></li><li> No penalties, no death, just take your time.<br></li><li> Collect hidden items for a (non-obligatory) 100% ending.<br></li><li> A short game (about 2 hours), focused on discovery and light puzzle solving.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335680/extras/eba23a6c4a3833f437f715de1d19d1d4.poster.avif?t=1626291185\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335680/extras/eba23a6c4a3833f437f715de1d19d1d4.webm?t=1626291185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335680/extras/eba23a6c4a3833f437f715de1d19d1d4.mp4?t=1626291185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
